N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 142.3 - Procedure upon transfer of a criminal case hereunder

State Regulations

Each case transferred from the Criminal

Court of the City of New York to the Supreme Court and referred for disposition
to the criminal division thereof pursuant to section
142.2
of this Part shall be
subject to the same substantive and procedural law as would have applied to it
had it not been transferred. Notes
